# Protocol Summary

| Category            | Requirement       |
| ------------------- | ----------------- |
| Command Case        | Lowercase only    |
| Encoding            | ASCII             |
| Response Terminator | `***`             |
| Parameter Separator | Space             |
| Decimal Display     | One decimal place |
| Persistent Settings | Temperature Limit |
| Log Capacity        | 5 entries         |
| State Values        | OK / OVERHEAT     |
